# ────────────────── QUICK ENVIRONMENT SWITCHING ──────────────────
# To switch to production:
# 1. Change NODE_ENV=production and VITE_NODE_ENV=production
# 2. All IPs will automatically use PRODUCTION_IP values
# 3. Uncomment production URLs in frontend .env if needed

# To switch to staging:
# 1. Change NODE_ENV=staging and VITE_NODE_ENV=staging
# 2. All IPs will automatically use STAGING_IP values